fields.calculatedFormula:
Records_To_Process__c = 0 &&
(
  GRAX_Schedule_Process__c = null || 
  ( 
    NOT(ISPICKVAL(GRAX_Schedule_Process__r.type__c, 'Hierarchy')) ||
    NOT(GRAX_Schedule_Process__r.Progressive__c)
  ) &&
  (
    (
      NOT(GRAX_Schedule_Process__r.Is_Running__c) &&
      DATEVALUE(CreatedDate) < TODAY() - 15
    ) ||
    (
      GRAX_Schedule_Process__r.Execution_Unique_Key__c != Execution_Unique_Key__c &&
      NOT(GRAX_Schedule_Process__r.Is_Running__c)
    ) ||
    (
      Records_Failed_to_Delete__c = 0 &&
      GRAX_Schedule_Process__r.Can_Delete_GRAX_Records__c &&
      (
        ISPICKVAL(Status__c, 'Sent Successful') ||
        (
          ISPICKVAL(Status__c, 'Not Sent') &&
          NOT(GRAX_Schedule_Process__r.Is_Running__c)
        )
      ) && 
      (
         ISBLANK(GRAX_Archive_Process__c) || 
         GRAX_Archive_Process__r.Can_Delete_GRAX_Record__c
      )
    )
  )
)
fields.label: Can Delete GRAX Record?
fields.name: Can_Delete_GRAX_Record__c
